Tuesday&#39;s event was attended by police officers from various units, including intervention groups from around the area - dozens of police officers who are commonly used to strengthen neighborhoods with higher levels of crime.
Mr Kelly explained that a large number of people came and went to the park during the day, so one hour a night was the perfect time to start the event.
