Military units meet with compassion rather than respect
The event was a gala evening on Wall Street that raised millions of dollars for New York war veterans without a roof over their heads.
Kid Rock sang the ballad about helplessness, frustration and loss.
Hundreds of soldiers, sailors, airmen and Marines gathered around him.
The festively dressed crowd stood up and applauded enthusiastically.
